# Temporary and intermediate files
Temp/

# Looper runtime state
**/Prompts/Inbox/Console.log
**/Prompts/Inbox/*/loop_state.json
**/Prompts/Inbox/routing_state.json

# Prompt files and results (runtime communication, not source code)
**/Prompts/Inbox/*/*.md

# Looper file attachments
**/Prompts/Inbox/*/Files/

# Windows Terminal layout state
wt_layout_state.json

# Looper lock files
.gateway.lock

# Python cache artifacts
**/__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd

# Telegram Gateway runtime state
Gateways/Telegram/gateway_delivery_state.json
Gateways/Telegram/sessions/

# Antigravity workspace
CorrisBot.code-workspace